entities.description: Service in the United States Armed Forces or Reserve components in a military combat zone or an area with imminent danger or hostile fire pay.
The general health status of an individual, stated as excellent, very good, good, fair, or poor.
The number of times an individual has moved in the past 12 months.
An individual's sexual orientation or attraction towards others.
